---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <p>
    Hecho a mano con <span class="accent">Astro</span> y código propio. Tipografía: <span class="accent">Inter</span> + <span class="accent">JetBrains Mono</span>.
  </p>
  <p>&copy; {year} Juan Unanue · Codemar</p>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .site-footer p { margin-bottom: 0.3rem; color: var(--text-muted); }

  .accent {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
</style>
